# gated access list - BLACKLIST by ASN (Autonomous System Number).
#
# One ASN per line, as "AS14061" or "14061". Blank lines and text
# after '#' are ignored. Requires geoip.enabled with an ASN database
# (geoip.asn_db). Blacklisting an ASN blocks ALL of that network's
# addresses — handy to cut off an abusive hosting/VPN provider.
#
# Examples (commented out):
# AS14061   # DigitalOcean
# AS16509   # Amazon AWS
# AS9009    # M247 (common VPN exit ranges)
